history.content: I am a junior EECS major currently signed up for these three courses next semester, but am starting to think it will be too much with the 3 weekly psets. I also know that when I have 3 heavier techs, one always ends up falling to the wayside so I can focus on the other two. As an aside, does anyone know anything about the workload about cs 182 (neural nets)? Would it be less than physics 7a, or is it better to just stick with 189 and 16b as my techs?
history.subject: cs 189, ee 16b, physics 7a course load?
